title: THURSDAY 5/20 - JALEN HURTS READY TO PAY THE RENT
itunes:title: THURSDAY 5/20 - JALEN HURTS READY TO PAY THE RENT
description:
Eagles QB Jalen Hurts (0:07) says he's ready for the competition for the starting job in Philly. 49ers GM John Lynch (0:57) says they were upfront with Jimmy Garoppolo on their plans to draft a QB. The Texans add another signal caller (1:51). Penei Sewell (2:19) signed, sealed and delivered in Detroit, and Antonio Brown (2:37) has knee surgery
